{"tid":1967361,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[超突發聲援] 4月11號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-04-11T00:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T00:41:38.000Z","uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42b13bef7434afc2aeb772ed2ad40bf87f3a66bf","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:38:16.000Z","msg":"🛑🛑🛑‼️突發提堂‼️🛑🛑🛑<br />\n<br />\n【#上庭聲援 - 4 月 1 1 日 星期六】<br />\n🕤09:30<br />\n🏛東 區 裁 判 法 院 6 樓 1 庭<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;⚖️錢禮主任裁判官<br />\n👤梁(16) #新案件 （#1013觀塘 管有攻擊性武器、未能出示身分證等）<br />\n<br />\n註**疫症期間法庭座位安排有限，如可行請先讓親友進入🙇🏻&zwj;♀️🙇🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"ae3c5717b7bdafcebe467b80d5934b9ad275d972","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:38:28.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=a9db0d74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"22ca31b1c421e454a45dc52e8f19ea8ebc54f7e6","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:38:38.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=553feb3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=244b2055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"c9a8227d9222b8e2da5617fc3f5c1f9b2a09eb5b","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhidZny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhidZny.jpg&h=182a5158&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b83822a5e5e017299261d27ca14c636560803bfa","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:39:03.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"043ef7e78c1c837d0a6fda1ea8f7fa21795f4f3e","tid":1967361,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:39:15.000Z","msg":"！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主好有心"},{"pid":"49794e6be0cfebe9eff2bbb0b8dc4e892f9e8581","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:39:24.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n東區裁判法院交通：<br />\n於「西灣河（嘉亨灣）巴士總站」落車<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n啟德：608<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中環、金鐘：720<br />\nCWB、天后、北角、太古：2<br />\n柴灣、赤柱：14<br />\n<br />\n於「鯉魚灣」巴士站落車<br />\n<strong>港島：</strong><br />\n中環：722<br />\nCWB、天后：2A,2X,77<br />\n北角、太古：2A,77,99,722<br />\n筲箕灣：2X,77,99<br />\n香港仔：77<br />\n海怡：99<br />\n<br />\n另外「西灣河碼頭」<br />\n有船來往觀塘碼頭，但旁邊係水警總部<br />\n<br />\n交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供"},{"pid":"13430f2f780f4e4ec55ec8371bf54af960854743","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"043ef7e78c1c837d0a6fda1ea8f7fa21795f4f3e","tid":1967361,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:39:15.000Z","msg":"！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主好有心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:39:49.000Z","msg":"多謝手足幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c900372a2498a39ce27afaa08118a5c8f419bbb1","tid":1967361,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T00:40:14.000Z","msg":"東區法院緊急要聲援師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079c93cc51c784b55e91a0612901932a8cf40d80","tid":1967361,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"